full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/28/2023 UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE IMMIGRATION AND NATURALIZATION SERVICE 7880 BISCAYNE BOULEVARD MIAMI, FLORIDA 33138 Date: April 14, 2000 Alien Number: A077912550 MARIE CHOISILIA DIEGUE 1355 NW 113 TER MIAMI, FL 33167 PLEASE BE ON TIME! A LATE ARRIVAL CAN CAUSE POSTPONEMENT OF YOUR INTERVIEW.
